)` call site via the public background-bootstrap API. It verifies:\n\n- A background bootstrap proxy is returned.\n- The proxy implements `SessionFactoryImplementor` and `InfrastructureProxy`.\n- `getProperties()` is handled by the Spring proxy without delegating to the target.\n- `getWrappedObject()` resolves to the bootstrapped target `SessionFactory`.\n- Regular `SessionFactory` methods delegate to the target.\n- The supplied `AsyncTaskExecutor` submits exactly one bootstrap task.\n\nPer instruction, I did not run tests locally.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fd855ec26e63a7b016a27148161708193a3e5203f2ebc82c8\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 344, "output": 538, "cacheRead": 25600, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26482, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780946039776, "responseId": "resp_0fd855ec26e63a7b016a2714784ee8819383787c69039c1112"}}
